p: In 2016, the top five high-incidence areas in Shenzhen were Guangming, Baoan, Longhua, Pingshan and Longgang, which had incidence rates of 492.70/100000, 426.12/100000, 415.88/100000, 367.31/100000, 323.28/1000000, respectively. The top five high-RR values areas were Yantian, Baoan, Guangming, Pingshan and Longgang, which had values of 5.28, 4.62, 3.59, 3.76 and 3.27, respectively. Although there were minor differences in the individual values, the basic order of the first five was consistent.
